Liam Brady (ex-Arsenal Head of Youth Development) on why the club let go of Harry Kane: &quot;He was a bit chubby, he wasn't very athletic but we made a mistake.&quot;<br />
<br />
Liam Brady on Arsenal releasing Harry Kane: &quot;Tottenham sent him out on loan to lower-division clubs three or four times as well. But through his determination he has carved out an amazing career and he deserves it.&quot;
